{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"171928-ihene-imbwa-n-inka","title":"Ihene, Imbwa, n'Inka","description":"Find out why the dog runs towards a car and a goat away from it!","language":"Kinyarwanda","langCode":"rw","isRtl":false,"level":"3","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Patrick Munyurangabo"],"illustrators":["Marleen  Visser"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/171928-ihene-imbwa-n-inka"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/230914/size3/7c81e4686ebc12ac21d75f2fb9275243.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/230914/size6/7c81e4686ebc12ac21d75f2fb9275243.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229559/size6/696a4cde242fd1345c447c05d4d61ce3.jpg","text":"Ihene, Imbwa, n'Inka bari\ninshuti magara.\nUmunsi umwe bagiye ku\nrugendo mu itagisi.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229561/size6/159e0859bd05f883a099d60b967267d3.jpg","text":"Basoje urugendo rwabo,\numushoferi yabasabye\nkwishyura.\nInka yatanze amafaranga\nyuzuye.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229563/size6/27be21a45a31a6c4af8ba391b2859b2a.jpg","text":"Imbwa\nyatanzearenzehokubera\nkoitari ifite avunje.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229565/size6/99ab5e99a86fa9fa0e946cb0fabf8269.jpg","text":"Umushoferiagiye\nkugarurira Imbwa ako\nkanya Ihene yarirutse\nigenda idatanze\namafaranga y'urugendo.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229566/size6/f7b8377e11e2ebc1c722bfe23dd2ce05.jpg","text":"Umushoferi yararakaye.\nYahise agenda\natagaruriye Imbwa.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229569/size6/2b544b24a81eb41a86c118c4dfd67879.jpg","text":"Iyi niyo mpanvu, kugeza\nnubu, Imbwa yirukanka\nisanga imodoka. Iba\nishaka kurebamo\numushoferi wagiye\natayigaruriye.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229571/size6/5cbfaf88f8247e98c59cd73aadfce9f3.jpg","text":"Ihene iyo yumvise\nimodoka ihinda iriruka.\nItinya ko bayifata kubera\nko itatanze amafaranga\ny'urugendo.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/229574/size6/6d813ebd24fa53e4cd6cb57ed8e16e58.jpg","text":"Inka yo ntacyo yikanga iyo\nimodoka ije.\nInka yambuka umuhanda\nyitonze kubera ko izi ko\nyatanze amafaranga\ny'urugendo.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":92}}